-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_returns.sql
```sql
-- Pick one approved return per item (earliest approved return)
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        item_id,
        return_id,
        return_date,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY CASE WHEN status = 'approved' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ASC,
            return_date ASC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    item_id,
    return_id,
    return_date,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

-- models/intermediate/int_items_with_categories.sql
```sql
-- Enrich items with product and category information
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        oi.item_id,
        oi.order_id,
        oi.product_id,
        oi.quantity,
        oi.unit_price,
        p.category_id,
        COALESCE(c.name, '(unknown)') AS category_name
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

-- models/intermediate/int_items_with_returns.sql
```sql
-- Identify which items have approved returns
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        ic.item_id,
        ic.category_name,
        CASE WHEN dr.item_id IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS is_returned
    FROM {{ ref('int_items_with_categories') }} ic
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} dr
        ON dr.item_id = ic.item_id
        AND dr.status = 'approved'
)
SELECT * FROM source
```

-- models/marts/fct_return_rate_by_category.sql
```sql
-- Calculate product return rates by category
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        category_name,
        COUNT(*) AS total_items_sold,
        SUM(is_returned) AS total_items_returned
    FROM {{ ref('int_items_with_returns') }}
    GROUP BY category_name
)
SELECT
    category_name,
    total_items_sold,
    total_items_returned,
    ROUND(CAST(total_items_returned AS DECIMAL(10,2)) / total_items_sold, 4) AS return_rate
FROM source
ORDER BY return_rate DESC
